'''asqqim unig n timmuzɣa''' ( s tfransit: le haut commissariat à l'amazighité )  iga timrslt takadimyt tunṣibt nna iswurin g yigr n tussna tamaziɣt deg tmurt n [[dzayer]]; ittuskr ass n 27 mayyu 1995. d timrslt tunṣibt tamzwarut yusin anzgum n tmaziɣt. teṭṭfat i uslway n dzayr nna tt isskrn dffir [[asalag n uqrab]], tfransist ( la grève du cartable),  nna gan inlmadn iqbayliyn. aslway nns amzwaru d [[muḥḥnd u yidir ayt ɛmṛan]] sg 1995 ar 2004. dɣi illa ɣifs [[yusf miraḥi]].

illa g tmaẓunt n dzayt. tawuri nns assidr n tutlayt, tamagit, taɣrma tamaziɣt. d ntta i iṭṭfurn asslmd n tutlayt tamaziɣt di dzayr. da issufuɣ awd kra n idlisn xf tmaziɣt d idls amaziɣ s umata. 


